title: Rigmar Radio Karaoke Collection 15200
description:
PLEASE DELETE ALL ENGELBERT HUMPERDINCK SONGS ON THE 14900 TORRENT.  There was a MP3 Meta Data error which resulted in the wrong spelling of the Artist name on about 50% of the songs.

I have corrected the tag information and re upped the whole lot in this torrent.

This sort of mistake is bound to happen on any very large collection, but I try and keep the errors to under 1% where possible.

300 CDG+MP3 Karaoke songs, a part of the 2015 Rigmar Radio commercial collection.

Rigmar Radio - Rockin' the Free World since 1967
